responses-copilot.config.modelTokenOverr:
Per-model token limit overrides. This has the highest priority and overrides built-in detection and global defaults.

Example:
```json
{
  "gpt-5": { "maxInputTokens": 272000, "maxOutputTokens": 128000 },
  "deepseek-v4-0324": { "maxInputTokens": 1000000, "maxOutputTokens": 384000 }
}
```
